<p>Since FixIt is based on LoveIt, migrating to Fixit is relatively easy. After some tweaking, the main changes to my website are as follows:</p>
<ol>
<li>Enable Twemoji</li>
<li>Migrate the comment system from Valine to Waline, add image and gif, article reactions, etc.</li>
