<li>Add Github corner</li>
<li>Change Mapbox map style</li>
<li>Add donation function</li>
<li>Add PWA support</li>
<li>Add website creation time display</li>
<li>Add BuSuanzi visit statistics</li>
<li>Add website word count</li>
<li>Change tags to word cloud display</li>
<li>Add PangguZhibai</li>
<li>Add page watermark</li>
<li>Add reading progress bar</li>
<li>Add page loading progress bar</li>
</ol>
<p>Now FixIt is still continuously and actively updating, and I will continue to follow up and continuously improve my website.</p>]]></description>
